code: @Test public void testExtractDirNameFromAbsolutePath() {     String path = "/test/depth1/myfile.txt".     assertEquals("myfile.txt", FtpUtils.extractDirNameFromAbsolutePath(path)).     path = "/test/depth1/myfile.txt/".     assertEquals("myfile.txt", FtpUtils.extractDirNameFromAbsolutePath(path)).     path = "test/depth1/".     assertEquals("depth1", FtpUtils.extractDirNameFromAbsolutePath(path)).     path = "test/depth1".     assertEquals("depth1", FtpUtils.extractDirNameFromAbsolutePath(path)).     path = "depth1".     assertEquals("depth1", FtpUtils.extractDirNameFromAbsolutePath(path)).     path = "\\test\\depth1\\myfile.txt".     assertEquals("myfile.txt", FtpUtils.extractDirNameFromAbsolutePath(path)).     path = "\\test\\depth1\\myfile.txt\\".     assertEquals("myfile.txt", FtpUtils.extractDirNameFromAbsolutePath(path)).     path = "test\\depth1\\".     assertEquals("depth1", FtpUtils.extractDirNameFromAbsolutePath(path)).     path = "test\\depth1".     assertEquals("depth1", FtpUtils.extractDirNameFromAbsolutePath(path)). }
